Name:           Black Wolf
Short Name:     wolf
Level Required: 1

Description:
  The weakest of all summoned creatures, the Wolf serves low-level
  Summoners very well, attacking with tooth and claw.

Commands:
  - summon wolf:    Summons it to you         (costs 10 sp)
  - catt <monster>: Makes it attack <monster> (costs 10 sp)
  - cstop:          Makes it stop fighting    (costs 20 sp)
  - ban wolf:       Banishes it               (costs 10 sp)
